CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FThe last known location of Noah
OL,7,FDonohoe's phone was relayed to search-
OL,8,Fand-rescue personnel seven hours after
OL,9,Fit was first received by police, an
OL,10,Finquest has heard.
OL,12,FSean McCarry, the Community Rescue
OL,13,FService (CRS) regional commander, told
OL,14,Fthe inquest into the death of the
OL,15,Fschoolboy that "time equals
OL,16,Fsurvivability" in searches and that he
OL,17,F"would expect" police to pass on all
OL,18,Frelevant information as soon as
OL,19,Fpossible.
OL,26,@wD@POUxD@NO]yD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FNoah was aged 14 when his naked body
OL,7,Fwas found in a storm drain tunnel in
OL,8,Fnorth Belfast, six days after he left
OL,9,Fhome on his bike to meet two friends
OL,10,Fin the Cavehill area in June 2020.
OL,12,FThe inquest at Belfast Coroner's
OL,13,FCourt, which is being heard with a
OL,14,Fjury, is in its fifth week.
OL,16,FMr McCarry told the inquest he felt
OL,17,F"massive responsibility as search
OL,18,Fmanager because a decision or lack of
OL,19,Fdecision, piece of information or lack
OL,20,Fof information is a difference of life
OL,21,Fand death".
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FHe reaffirmed the importance of his
OL,7,Forganisation getting information as
OL,8,Fsoon as possible from the police and
OL,9,Fsaid this would have been standard
OL,10,Fpractice.
OL,12,FDuring questioning by counsel for
OL,13,FNoah's mother Fiona Donohoe, Brenda
OL,14,FCampbell KC, Mr McCarry did stress
OL,15,Fthat if he felt there was a piece of
OL,16,Finformation he needed he "probably
OL,17,Fwould have become quite a pain until I
OL,18,Fgot it".
OL,26,@xD@ZOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
