CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FHe was first called out by police at
OL,7,Fapproximately 3.40am on June 22, Noah
OL,8,Fhaving been reported missing by his
OL,9,Fmother on the evening of June 21.
OL,11,FOn this initial call, he said he was
OL,12,Fgiven "nothing else" from police to
OL,13,Fsuggest they should search anywhere
OL,14,Fbut Cavehill, but that this was not
OL,15,Fout of the ordinary as it "would be
OL,16,Fdifficult enough at 3am in the morning
OL,17,Fto have immediate CCTV".
OL,26,@tD@GOUtD@TO]wD@[OUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FIt was established, during
OL,7,Fquestioning, that when the CRS
OL,8,Freceived information from police
OL,9,Faround 11am on June 22 from the TLU
OL,10,F(Telecoms Liaison Unit) giving an
OL,11,Fupdated location as to where Noah's
OL,12,Fphone was last located, search teams
OL,13,Fwere deployed to that area but that
OL,14,Fsearching also continued around
OL,15,FCavehill.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FMr McCarry said it was "quite
OL,7,Fuplifting and quite reassuring" to get
OL,8,Fsome more information and that when
OL,9,FCCTV emerged later, North Queen Street
OL,10,Fbecame Noah's official "place last
OL,11,Fseen".
OL,13,FHe added that at this stage, search
OL,14,Foperations would still have been
OL,15,F"heavily reliant" on information from
OL,16,Fpolice.
OL,26,@nD@XOUoD@_O]rD@XOUsD@EO]wD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FMs Campbell said that police failed to
OL,7,Fspot Noah on the CCTV procured at
OL,8,FGrove Leisure Centre and showed jurors
OL,9,Fa map that would have been produced if
OL,10,Fthat location had become Noah's place
OL,11,Flast seen, that would have taken in
OL,12,FNorthwood Road where his body was
OL,13,Feventually found, as well as where his
OL,14,Fbike and helmet were located.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FMr McCarry said if that information
OL,7,Fwas available, they "would have
OL,8,Fdeployed another team" into that area
OL,9,Fand "certainly would have found those
OL,10,Fitems, they were in sight of
OL,11,Feveryone", adding that it "may well
OL,12,Fhave" led searchers to Northwood Road
OL,13,Fsooner.
OL,15,FMs Campbell presented a hypothetical
OL,16,Fto Mr McCarry, asking if they "might
OL,17,Fhave been down culvert at 9am" on June
OL,18,F22, had they been given the TLU
OL,19,Finformation and corresponding CCTV
OL,20,Fwhen he was first called.
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@VO]qD@EOUsD@IO]sD@[OUtD@EO]xD@
OL,26,A_OUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FMr McCarry replied: "Hypothetically,
OL,7,Fyes, but there has to be a balance."
OL,9,FMs Campbell said "if things are
OL,10,Fmissed, they need to be exposed to
OL,11,Fpublic scrutiny", and Mr McCarry
OL,12,Fresponded "yes and fixed", adding: "I
OL,13,Ffully support that if anything can be
OL,14,Fchanged, I want to understand what
OL,15,Fthat is so it never happens again."
OL,17,FThe inquest was then shown an email
OL,18,Ffrom a TLU officer to PSNI officers
OL,19,Fworking on Noah's case on June 22 at
OL,20,F3.18am, attaching a location found
OL,21,Ffrom his mobile at 7.41pm on June 21.
OL,26,@nD@UOUoD@dO]qD@ROUsD@PO]tD@KOUtD@YO]tD@
OL,26,AdOUwD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FThe corresponding log from the TLU
OL,7,Fshowed that the police were also
OL,8,Fcalled to ensure receipt and
OL,9,Funderstanding of this email.
OL,11,FMr McCarry said he was seeing this for
OL,12,Fthe first time and that he was under
OL,13,Fthe impression that when it was
OL,14,Fpresented to him at 11am on June 22,
OL,15,Fit was a new development.
OL,17,FHe said he "would expect that" it
OL,18,Fwould have been sent when received by
OL,19,Fpolice.
OL,26,@yD@LOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FMs Campbell suggested that if he had
OL,7,Fthat location at 4am, he "wouldn't
OL,8,Fnecessarily have been putting boots in
OL,9,FCavehill in the same numbers".
OL,11,FMr McCarry said he "can't disagree
OL,12,Fwith that", adding it "may not have
OL,13,Fmade a difference, but we don't know
OL,14,Fthat".
OL,16,FMs Campbell said: "Noah's mum doesn't
OL,17,Fknow why at four o'clock in the
OL,18,Fmorning, you weren't told about that
OL,19,FTLU map and neither do you."
OL,21,FMr McCarry said that was correct.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUqD@]O]sD@TOUtD@JO]tD@WOUvD@EO]xD@
OL,26,ASOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772216417
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe phone location relayed to
OL,4,Csearchers after seven hours ` inquest
OL,6,FMs Campbell added that Ms Donohoe and
OL,7,FMr McCarry were both unaware as to why
OL,8,Fthe TLU map "wasn't urgently married
OL,9,Fup with CCTV in those early-morning
OL,10,Fhours".
OL,12,FMr McCarry agreed with Ms Campbell's
OL,13,Frestatement of his earlier testimony
OL,14,Fthat "delay can be the difference
OL,15,Fbetween time and death" in missing
OL,16,Fperson searches.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
